Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.86,0:22:25.32,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(150,150)}着いたら教えて
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.45,0:22:27.24,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(150,150)}使い慣れたスタンプで
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.49,0:22:29.87,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(150,150)}話合えちゃうスタンスが本当
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.07,0:22:33.62,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(150,150)}心地良くて愛しい
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.12,0:22:37.67,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(150,150)}一人胸にしまいこんだ言葉も
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.29,0:22:41.92,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(150,150)}上手くいかない減らない悩み事も
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.30,0:22:48.34,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(150,150)}全部忘れて遊びに行きたいね
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.76,0:22:54.85,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(150,150)}心のメモリア
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.85,0:22:57.94,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(150,150)}笑顔が溢れるよ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.23,0:23:02.15,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(150,150)}冗談混じりで頷く
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.36,0:23:06.07,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(150,150)}何気ないありふれたやり取りが
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.24,0:23:11.28,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(150,150)}心のメモリア
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.28,0:23:14.37,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(150,150)}涙が零れても
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.66,0:23:16.87,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(150,150)}頑張れるよ
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.87,0:23:20.58,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(150,150)}君がくれた今日が
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.83,0:23:23.42,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(150,150)}優しくてありがとう
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.42,0:23:24.88,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(150,150)}Let's hang out
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.46,0:23:29.30,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(150,150)}I wanna talk with you
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.77,0:22:19.56,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(150,150)}约好的时间是几点（十点）
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.81,0:22:21.73,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(150,150)}在车站前集合（OK）
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.86,0:22:25.32,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(150,150)}到了就告诉我
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.45,0:22:27.24,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(150,150)}能够拿用惯了的表情
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.49,0:22:29.87,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(150,150)}来交谈心事的关系
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.07,0:22:33.62,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(150,150)}实在让人舒心爱怜
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.12,0:22:37.67,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(150,150)}独自藏在自己心里的话语
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.29,0:22:41.92,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(150,150)}过得不顺 越来越多的烦心事
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.30,0:22:48.34,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(150,150)}想要全都忘掉 和你一起出去玩
